+	 * + task_number lets the PC sequencer run them back-to-back with a continuous
+	 * ping-pong. The old per-task dispatch (one OP_EN each) left the FIRST task of
+	 * every kick on a cold PP, so it never engaged (CORE_OPEN=0). Mark all tasks
